  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bae\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9c\u0ba9 \u0baa\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bc1\u0ba9\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd : \u0b9a\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bb0 \u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dissatisfied with the government led by Prime Minister Ranil, Budujana Peramuna: Sagara Kariyavasam",
      "author": "Digital Desk 5",
      "body_lines": [
        "Most of the members of the Podujana Peramuna have expressed their dissatisfaction with the government led by Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe. Political instability will exacerbate current crises.",
        "Sagara Kariyawasam, General Secretary of Podujana Peramuna stated that we will urge the President to establish a government led by Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna.",
        "A meeting between President Gotabaya Rajapaksa and members of Podujana Peramuna will be held at the President's House today.",
        "The ruling party committee meeting between members of the Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna and President Gotabaya Rajapaksa will be held at the President's House today.",
        "The government has failed to find a solution to the crises that have intensified in the social structure. While Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe has mentioned that there are no alternative plans except to get the cooperation of the International Monetary Fund, it can be observed that the International Monetary Fund has imposed many conditions regarding the cooperation of Sri Lanka.",
        "If the conditions of the International Monetary Fund are implemented, the middle class will suffer more. The main shortcoming is that the parties who highlight only the positive factors of the IMF do not publicize the negative factors.",
        "We supported the government led by United National Party leader Ranil Wickremesinghe to solve the basic problems faced by the people of the country. There is doubt whether the current government - led by the Lanka Podujana Peramuna.",
        "The economy is affected by various factors. The Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna-led government has a responsibility to protect the mandate given by the people.",
        "We urge the President to establish a Sri Lanka Podujana Peramuna-led government. He said that if the political mistakes are not corrected now, it will affect the future political existence."
      ],
